{"tid":1561694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家開心完就繼續做返正經事啦","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:56.000Z","uid":216995,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81e3bc8837ba9ba955d452c0140110246d4ae8db","tid":1561694,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"正所謂物極必反，如果抗爭太過崩緊，就會好多人支撐唔到落去。所以適當嘅娛樂是必要的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係如果沉迷娛樂一樣都會物極必反，造成運動失焦，回到雨革。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家記住，我地仲有一千幾個義士等住我哋去救。仲有在天之靈嘅手足等我們幫佢哋完成佢哋嘅遺願。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以真係實現到係煲底下除口罩互相相認的願望，而唔係自我FF.<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不分化不指責。我知有啲手足有時候會睇唔過眼，但仍然希望大家可以以提點嘅方式。<br />\n<br />\n中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee46ac5094bd6db494fdbe3f1bc80202aa3d3cd","tid":1561694,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"自推十連！"},{"pid":"a40006b7de5e36be79140a54196e5630cd507776","tid":1561694,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0a481056833a356f1ff306e319ed47e628ff11c","tid":1561694,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?